      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-exe-rou-srt    =    spaces
                     go to main-400
           else      go to main-500.
       main-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se sort non eseguito                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ciclo di report-program                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   prn-rou-pri-000      thru prn-rou-pri-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Continuazione                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     main-600.
       main-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se sort eseguito                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Continuazione                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     main-600.
       main-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
