      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test                                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rr-tmo-ftr           not  = spaces        and
                     rr-tmo-ftr           not  = rf-fit-cod-tmo
                     go to sel-fit-rec-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Bufferizzazione codice                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-fit-cod-tmo       to   w-sel-fit-cod-tmo      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Lettura                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-fit-cod-tmo       to   w-let-arc-zfi-cod      .
           perform   let-arc-zfi-000      thru let-arc-zfi-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
