      *                      * Descrizione                             *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-zfi-des    to   w-sel-fit-des-tmo      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Flag di codice esistente                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-zfi-flg    to   w-sel-fit-flg-tmo      .
