      *                  * Subroutine di selezione                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   sel-fit-rec-scd-000  thru sel-fit-rec-scd-999    .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test sul flag di uscita dalla subrotine     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-sel-fit-scd-exi    not  = spaces
                     go to sel-fit-rec-900.
       sel-fit-rec-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
