                     go to sel-fit-rec-scd-900.
       sel-fit-rec-scd-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Max su [sdb]                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-sdb-prt-fcl       not  = rf-fit-num-prt
                     go to sel-fit-rec-scd-900.
       sel-fit-rec-scd-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Selezione su tipo scadenza                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
