           go to     sel-fit-rec-scd-600.
       sel-fit-rec-scd-405.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo scadenza : Solo Rimesse Dirette        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-sdb-tip-sdb       =    01 and
                     rf-sdb-snx-dlc       =    "N"
