                     move  spaces         to   kk0-dpz-cli
           else      move  srt-cod-cli-dpz
                                          to   kk0-dpz-cli            .
           read      kk0    invalid key
                            go to   agg-abc-kk0-575.
           go to     agg-abc-kk0-600.
       agg-abc-kk0-575.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
